22.body:
this function will store a temporary value in the code that will go away once its done running, you input the name of the variable which is what you will use in $val{name} to output the [value] which will be whatever you want the value to be. Example: $var(a['100']);
$output.console{$val{a}}; this would output 100 in the console.
